#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn22.126"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn22.126:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 22 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 22 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.126:0.2"
msgid "13. Avijjāvagga "
msgstr "13. Ignorance "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn22.126:0.3"
msgid "126. Samudayadhammasutta "
msgstr "126. Liable To Originate "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli3.171, sc1
msgctxt "sn22.126:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.126:1.2"
msgid "Atha kho aññataro bhikkhu yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā … pe … ekamantaṃ nisinno kho so bhikkhu bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "Then a mendicant went up to the Buddha, bowed, sat down to one side, and said to him: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.126:1.3"
msgid "“‘avijjā, avijjā’ti, bhante, vuccati. "
msgstr "“Sir, they speak of this thing called ‘ignorance’. "

msgctxt "sn22.126:1.4"
msgid "Katamā nu kho, bhante, avijjā; "
msgstr "What is ignorance? "

msgctxt "sn22.126:1.5"
msgid "kittāvatā ca avijjāgato hotī”ti? "
msgstr "And how is an ignorant person defined?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn22.126:2.1"
msgid "“Idha, bhikkhu, assutavā puthujjano samudayadhammaṃ rūpaṃ ‘samudayadhammaṃ rūpan’ti yathābhūtaṃ nappajānāti; "
msgstr "“Mendicant, it’s when an uneducated ordinary person doesn’t truly understand form, which is liable to originate, as form which is liable to originate. "

msgctxt "sn22.126:2.2"
msgid "vayadhammaṃ rūpaṃ ‘vayadhammaṃ rūpan’ti yathābhūtaṃ nappajānāti; "
msgstr "They don’t truly understand form, which is liable to vanish, as form which is liable to vanish. "

msgctxt "sn22.126:2.3"
msgid "samudayavayadhammaṃ rūpaṃ ‘samudayavayadhammaṃ rūpan’ti yathābhūtaṃ nappajānāti. "
msgstr "They don’t truly understand form, which is liable to originate and vanish, as form which is liable to originate and vanish. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.126:2.4"
msgid "Samudayadhammaṃ vedanaṃ ‘samudayadhammā vedanā’ti yathābhūtaṃ nappajānāti; "
msgstr "They don’t truly understand feeling … "

msgctxt "sn22.126:2.5"
msgid "vayadhammaṃ vedanaṃ ‘vayadhammā vedanā’ti yathābhūtaṃ nappajānāti; "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn22.126:2.6"
msgid "samudayavayadhammaṃ vedanaṃ ‘samudayavayadhammā vedanā’ti yathābhūtaṃ nappajānāti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn22.126:2.7"
msgid "Samudayadhammaṃ saññaṃ … pe … "
msgstr "perception … "

msgctxt "sn22.126:2.8"
msgid "samudayadhamme saṅkhāre ‘samudayadhammā saṅkhārā’ti yathābhūtaṃ nappajānāti; "
msgstr "choices … "

msgctxt "sn22.126:2.9"
msgid "vayadhamme saṅkhāre ‘vayadhammā saṅkhārā’ti yathābhūtaṃ nappajānāti; "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn22.126:2.10"
msgid "samudayavayadhamme saṅkhāre ‘samudayavayadhammā saṅkhārā’ti yathābhūtaṃ nappajānāti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn22.126:2.11"
msgid "Samudayadhammaṃ viññāṇaṃ ‘samudayadhammaṃ viññāṇan’ti yathābhūtaṃ nappajānāti; "
msgstr "consciousness, which is liable to originate, as consciousness which is liable to originate. "

msgctxt "sn22.126:2.12"
msgid "vayadhammaṃ viññāṇaṃ ‘vayadhammaṃ viññāṇan’ti yathābhūtaṃ nappajānāti; "
msgstr "They don’t truly understand consciousness, which is liable to vanish, as consciousness which is liable to vanish. "

msgctxt "sn22.126:2.13"
msgid "samudayavayadhammaṃ viññāṇaṃ ‘samudayavayadhammaṃ viññāṇan’ti yathābhūtaṃ nappajānāti. "
msgstr "They don’t truly understand consciousness, which is liable to originate and vanish, as consciousness which is liable to originate and vanish. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.126:2.14"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhu, avijjā; "
msgstr "This is called ignorance. "

msgctxt "sn22.126:2.15"
msgid "ettāvatā ca avijjāgato hotī”ti. "
msgstr "And this is how an ignorant person is defined.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "sn22.126:3.1"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, so bhikkhu bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "When he said this, the mendicant said to the Buddha: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.126:3.2"
msgid "“‘vijjā, vijjā’ti, bhante, vuccati. "
msgstr "“Sir, they speak of this thing called ‘knowledge’. "

msgctxt "sn22.126:3.3"
msgid "Katamā nu kho, bhante, vijjā; "
msgstr "What is knowledge? "

msgctxt "sn22.126:3.4"
msgid "kittāvatā ca vijjāgato hotī”ti? "
msgstr "And how is a knowledgeable person defined?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli3.172, sc4
msgctxt "sn22.126:4.1"
msgid "“Idha, bhikkhu, sutavā ariyasāvako samudayadhammaṃ rūpaṃ ‘samudayadhammaṃ rūpan’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti; "
msgstr "“Mendicant, it’s when an educated noble disciple truly understands form, which is liable to originate, as form which is liable to originate. "

msgctxt "sn22.126:4.2"
msgid "vayadhammaṃ rūpaṃ ‘vayadhammaṃ rūpan’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti; "
msgstr "They truly understand form, which is liable to vanish, as form which is liable to vanish. "

msgctxt "sn22.126:4.3"
msgid "samudayavayadhammaṃ rūpaṃ ‘samudayavayadhammaṃ rūpan’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti. "
msgstr "They truly understand form, which is liable to originate and vanish, as form which is liable to originate and vanish. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.126:4.4"
msgid "Samudayadhammaṃ vedanaṃ ‘samudayadhammā vedanā’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti; "
msgstr "They truly understand feeling … "

msgctxt "sn22.126:4.5"
msgid "vayadhammaṃ vedanaṃ ‘vayadhammā vedanā’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti; "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn22.126:4.6"
msgid "samudayavayadhammaṃ vedanaṃ ‘samudayavayadhammā vedanā’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn22.126:4.7"
msgid "Samudayadhammaṃ saññaṃ … "
msgstr "perception … "

msgctxt "sn22.126:4.8"
msgid "samudayadhamme saṅkhāre ‘samudayadhammā saṅkhārā’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti; "
msgstr "choices … "

msgctxt "sn22.126:4.9"
msgid "vayadhamme saṅkhāre ‘vayadhammā saṅkhārā’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti; "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn22.126:4.10"
msgid "samudayavayadhamme saṅkhāre ‘samudayavayadhammā saṅkhārā’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn22.126:4.11"
msgid "Samudayadhammaṃ viññāṇaṃ ‘samudayadhammaṃ viññāṇan’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti; "
msgstr "consciousness, which is liable to originate, as consciousness which is liable to originate. "

msgctxt "sn22.126:4.12"
msgid "vayadhammaṃ viññāṇaṃ ‘vayadhammaṃ viññāṇan’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti; "
msgstr "They truly understand consciousness, which is liable to vanish, as consciousness which is liable to vanish. "

msgctxt "sn22.126:4.13"
msgid "samudayavayadhammaṃ viññāṇaṃ ‘samudayavayadhammaṃ viññāṇan’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti. "
msgstr "They truly understand consciousness, which is liable to originate and vanish, as consciousness which is liable to originate and vanish. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.126:4.14"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhu, vijjā; "
msgstr "This is called knowledge. "

msgctxt "sn22.126:4.15"
msgid "ettāvatā ca vijjāgato hotī”ti. "
msgstr "And this is how a knowledgeable person is defined.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn22.126:4.16"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

